      "writtenOn": "2017-01-24T16:43:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think it would be useful to make an interface for specs.TempGitRepo, e.g.:\n\ntype Checkouter interface {\n  Checkout(rs db.RepoState) (*git.TempCheckout, error)\n}\nand pass this in to TaskScheduler. You can then easily mock it instead of downloading all of depot_tools for each TS test and parsing command lines in tests. Also, it will be easier to think about more complex implementations (e.g. worker pools) if TempGitRepo is an interface rather than a function.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 58,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 59,
        "endChar": 24
      },
      "revId": "cdf15d7965a890ba8f8cef877d9a71d3b9e3fbaf",
